\begin{document}
}{}$zeros$\end{document}</tex-math></inline-formula>, where each row corresponds to the possible nucleotides (A, C, T, G or N) and the columns represent the bases present in the sequence of length <inline-formula><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="ImEquation16">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
